  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add walnuts and garlic to the pan. Toast for about 2 minutes or until fragrant.",
    "Stir in butternut squash puree, almond butter, and red pepper flakes. Cook for an additional 3-4 minutes, stirring frequently to prevent sticking.",
    "Toss cooked penne rigate into the skillet with the nutty mix-ins. Cook for about 2 minutes or until pasta is heated through.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley before serving."
